headline: Aitech’s SP1 SpaceVPX SBC Showcases Strategic Integration of Teledyne’s Advanced Space Computing Capabilities
summary: CHATSWORTH, Calif. & GRENOBLE, France, February 18, 2026--Aitech and Teledyne e2v Semiconductors are proud to highlight their continued collaboration in advancing space-grade computing. Through their ongoing partnership, Teledyne e2v’s high-reliability semiconductors are being integrated into Aitech’s SP1, a radiation-tolerant 3U SpaceVPX single-board computer (SBC).
